I've followed her for some time now and I've noticed a pattern/cycle here.

I'm starting to suspect that her metabolism is ruined from the high intensity training and starving herself, so that's why she keeps gaining the weight back despite all the effort. 
I was like her last year, but I stopped. Ironically, once I intuitively eat and do strength training(also some cardio), I achieved my dream physique. Now I'm at a stable weight and I can still eat what I want.
I hope she finds her golden middle before falling into insanity.
